01:12:47,280 --> 01:12:51,114
Cak ni odeca koju nosim
nije moja.

638
01:12:51,320 --> 01:12:54,869
Nisam cak ni radio
da bih dobio ovu sedu kosu.

639
01:12:55,080 --> 01:12:58,834
l, ja ne volim lažnjake...

640
01:13:00,600 --> 01:13:04,388
